25
00:04:32,782 --> 00:04:44,358
mutually cutting each other on the high seas, like a brace of dandies in Broadway, and all the time indulging perhaps in finical criticism upon each other's rig.

26
00:04:44,378 --> 00:05:01,742
As for men of war, when they chance to meet at sea, they first go through such a string of silly bowings and scrapings, such a ducking of ensigns, that there does not seem to be much write-down hearty good-will and brotherly love about it at all.

27
00:05:01,992 --> 00:05:17,740
