40
00:06:53,966 --> 00:06:54,888
But what is a gamb?

41
00:06:55,569 --> 00:07:01,763
You might wear out your index finger running up and down the columns of dictionaries and never find the word.

42
00:07:02,504 --> 00:07:05,871
Dr. Johnson never attains to that erudition.

43
00:07:06,373 --> 00:07:08,878
Noah Webster's Ark does not hold it.

44
00:07:08,858 --> 00:07:17,533
Nevertheless, this same expressive word has now, for many years, been in constant use among some 15,000 true-born Yankees.

45
00:07:18,274 --> 00:07:22,721
Certainly it needs a definition, and should be incorporated into the lexicon.

46
00:07:23,523 --> 00:07:26,648
With that view, let me learnedly define it.

47
00:07:26,628 --> 00:07:27,249
Damn!

48
